Getting Started with Mavely
Frequently Asked Questions
How do I get started on Mavely?
It’s easy to join Mavely as an Everyday Influencer. Sign up, verify your account, and you’re ready to get started. There’s no fee or application.
How can I make money as an influencer?
Earn on Mavely through affiliate links, brand campaigns, monthly bonuses, and referral commission.
Do I need a high follower count to sign up?
No! You can join and be successful on Mavely with whatever audience size you have. There’s no application to get started.
I don't consider myself an influencer. Will this still work for me?
Yes! Mavely technology lets you easily create shoppable SmartLinks that you can share anywhere. You earn money whenever friends, family, or followers buy products from your link.
